h2-how-to-set-up-splitmetrics-acquire-in.translation:
## 如何配置 SplitMetrics Acquire 集成 \{#how-to-set-up-splitmetrics-acquire-integration\}

要集成 SplitMetrics Acquire，请前往 [Integrations > SplitMetrics Acquire](https://app.adapty.io/integrations/splitmetrics) 并填写凭证信息。

